地制度，但<span class=\"red\">他們需認識</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不直接教愛國 「多學國情毋須認同」<br />\n<br />\n陳又說，<span class=\"red\">當日「國家安全教育中心」流動展覽車會到訪學校，介紹國家主席習近平提出的「總體國家安全觀」</span>。翻查資料，該中心去年底<span class=\"red\">由建制派立法會議員何君堯牽頭成立</span>，目標包括推動《基本法》23條立法。<br />\n<br />\n呢間學校有幾紅?<br />\n呢間西門英才中學搞乜尻？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2416971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2416971</a>"},{"pid":"fe4c02bb86a985c921add18f2074d3e2c71a9a39","tid":2486631,"uid":268146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"755439501b1cf410270ee542a3ad64156f09eaba","tid":2486631,"uid":374269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"有冇其他中小學都有推廣國安教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎開佢名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢, 係咪 4月15日唔做任何嘢嘅學校先會俾人批鬥???"},{"pid":"7ce7b9a1e08c2c5be6bada3de5a21cd6eec35d2b","tid":2486631,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T07:22:00.000Z","msg":"其實好多中學已經有專人負責統籌同推行國安教育<br />\n教育局一早落咗order"},{"pid":"0513c28b1fc74cc4fefb212031a634aba089ecdf","tid":2486631,"uid":295279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb1c40196cf8e23520f4438fe6ee30c31c9b5f9e","tid":2486631,"uid":374269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55bf01fce7b408ce54e156b90627d75dd3c269a","tid":2486631,"uid":57488,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"蘇浙公學<br />\n個名已經講咗比你知有幾紅<br />\n同福建中學嗰啲根本同類嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ok491B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ok491B.png&h=7ba25e47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3ZmsOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3ZmsOg.png&h=c0d1a2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.schooland.hk/ss